In this episode of So This Happened, we reviewed the application for the extradition of former IRT boss, DCP Abba Kyari to the United States for his involvement with Hushpuppi over alleged fraud. We also reviewed the invasion of Ukraine by Russia and the fallouts. The evacuation of
